    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "67c",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "September 17, 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Federal Bureau of Investigation",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Washington, D. C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Dear Sirs:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "At 3:40 P.M. to-day I observed a so-called flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "saucer. This occurred while I was half way up Rix Ledges",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "north of Lebanon, N. H. As I was intently watching the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "honey bees circling in a patch of sky after leaving my",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "bee box my attention was called to a floating object that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "appeared to be as large as a tennis ball and as white as",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "cotton batting. This object approached rapidly and noiselessly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "from the East and was followed closely by another object",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "that appeared in size and shape like a saucer which maintained",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "a constant angle of inclination to the ball and followed it",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "at a constant distance. The two objects made an angle with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "my eye of approximately five degrees. They were in my vision",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "for more than a minute when I lost them in the glare of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "sun.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "If I had seen this in the night sky with my six inch",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "telescope I would have thought that the planets Venus and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "Saturn had suddenly gotten together and were traveling",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "at great speed much nearer the earth. 6-85191-75",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
